SnowBlozm 
PHP Service Computing Platform
http://snowblozm.blogspot.com/

Simplified Service Oriented Architecture
Vibhaj Rajan
vibhaj8@gmail.com

Features 
	Snowblozm Experimental Service Computing Platform 		for executing services and workflows
	Snowblozm Reference Framework 				for managing application entities
	Snowblozm Key-Chain-Web Mechanism 			for access control
	Snowblozm Application Layer Security 			for access security

